{"tid":2036572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"滯留安哥拉的中國人當街哭訴「懇求中國讓我們回家」，公然抹黑祖國","createTime":"2020-05-26T14:07:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T16:14:48.000Z","uid":48040,"like":114,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"a96eb00a1143000879cc4c8028bad78083135803","tid":2036572,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T14:07:55.000Z","msg":"中國目前推出「五個一」的防疫政策，即「一家航空公司」只能有「一條航線」從「一個國家」飛來中國，「一週」只準「一班機」。這導致國際航班票價飛漲，英美飛到中國的機票需要數萬元，大量中國人被自己的祖國拒之門外。<br />\n於是，這些滯留在安哥拉的中國人，居然在別人的國家，用中文掛出標語：「懇求中國讓我們回家」。<br />\n這些中國人，通過這種喪心病狂的方式，肆意抹黑中國，破壞社會秩序，勢必會被全國愛國民眾的唾棄。民眾的眼睛是雪亮的，現在機票貴不貴，不是由這一小撮背棄祖國的人決定的。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6Dv7XM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6Dv7XM.jpg&h=4da159da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n=====<br />\n五毛話呢個channel的follower冇可能過一萬。你可以幫幫手嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QunCLp8421g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQunCLp8421g&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMA3jCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=dd93b239\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QunCLp8421g</a>"},{"pid":"e23bd16e50ab6a9f8cbe26dcd3a216f17f179f8b","tid":2036572,"uid":128102,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T14:17:53.000Z","msg":"call戰狼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c852901c551fac7f514522bb027316f3abf1111f","tid":2036572,"uid":48040,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"e23bd16e50ab6a9f8cbe26dcd3a216f17f179f8b","tid":2036572,"uid":128102,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T14:17:53.000Z","msg":"call戰狼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T14:18:33.000Z","msg":"又話中國護照可以從天涯海角把國民帶回家"},{"pid":"d9ad13815f852aaedebe92988a83c69543772348","tid":2036572,"uid":48040,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T14:19:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YbW2hf5.jpg\"